title: More fan art than you could imagine.
content:
And no it's not from me.

Many months ago (years even?) Deviant Art removed their search feature because they needed to replace it with a less bandwidth eating system. Today they released the beta for the new search. What was the first thing I looked for?

Commander Keen of course! [url=http://search.deviantart.com/searchcraft/?cmd=1&search=%22Commander+Keen%22&offset=0]Linkey[/url]

I was surprised to see so many people who did fan art. Most of it is really good too.-----------------------
"The Adventures of Commander Keen" issue #1: [img]http://img93.imageshack.us/img93/8904/wid1kx.png[/img]
"Fat people buy lots"

title: haha
content: Neat!  Many of those are RocketJess's, and a few others have been posted by their respective artists, before the board loss.  There's a few new ones in there, too.  Good find!
